- [ ] All 6 test blocks pass (2 no-op cases, 1 parameterised table with 11 rows, 1 forward-compat, 1 aria-label, 1 test id) — 16 assertions total.
- [ ] Test file uses `@vitest-environment jsdom` and cleans up with `afterEach(cleanup)`.
- [ ] `pnpm vitest run apps/client/src/layers/features/chat/__tests__/TerminalReasonChip.test.tsx` reports zero failures.
